examples.verbose_instruction:
To finish this task, please follow these steps:

1. Click the "New" button on the top right;
2. Choose "SQL Query" in the drop-down panel;
3. Copy the SQL query in 'question1.sql' file and paste it in input panel.
4. Click the "Run query" button on the right side, and check the output data.
5. Click on "Save" button on the top right corner;
6. Type in "question1" under "name", and click "Save".
7. Click on "Yes please!".
8. Click on the button "Create a new dashboard";
9. Type in "New Dashboard" under "name", and click "Create".
10. Click on "Save" button on the top right corner;
